{"tid":1771486,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"申請分期繳稅須提供三個月財務文件證明財困","createTime":"2019-12-06T01:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T09:28:09.000Z","uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"89b9ca9b09bbed14e255f955e072007a297bd4ae","tid":1771486,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"政府早前公布第四輪紓困措施，其中包括2018/19年度之利得稅、薪俸稅或個人入息稅可申請分期繳付稅項，並豁免附加費。<br />\n<br />\n稅務局昨日(5日)公布，申請人需要證明因財政困難導致未能按時交稅，同時須提交最近三個月的銀行存摺、月結單副本、收支表及相關證明文件。經營業務者亦要提交最近三個月之管理賬目，並須列出具體分期繳稅建議。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，將因應個別申請的經濟狀況批出不同還款期的分期繳稅安排，並承諾在收到申請後的21個工作天內回覆申請人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.980711/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.980711%2F2&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScHG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=2b33202e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.980711/2</a>"},{"pid":"4e30821a8de12e11ed39ad95ca39d2c987f79978","tid":1771486,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"比稅比政府打自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f11513f6c180463143ef189541fb1de3894dc4","tid":1771486,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:58:05.000Z","msg":"笑撚人 行政費一定貴撚到"},{"pid":"aaffa9d54105de0079e83a7cec74e659e46716a6","tid":1771486,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:59:14.000Z","msg":"分期交都咁撚煩，乜撚野紓困措施黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf180a2c7847c741b569dca89b1c5fce5a4ff3a3","tid":1771486,"uid":60362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"要交稅就唔財困啦，on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c1e6da992affcd3b9f43c3e8364162c73dbd19","tid":1771486,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite